OL,3,CHow is climate change and river
OL,4,Cpollution shaking up the Senedd
OL,5,CElection?
OL,7,FCandidates in the upcoming Senedd
OL,8,Felection have been out on the campaign
OL,9,Ftrail across Wales, with some voters
OL,10,Fyet to make their minds up about which
OL,11,Fparty they will vote for on May 7th.
OL,13,FSo far in the campaign we have heard
OL,14,Ffrom voters who will choose where they
OL,15,Fput their X on the ballot paper based
OL,16,Fon their experiences with the health
OL,17,Fservice, and their views on
OL,18,Fimmigration.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
