OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1777039866
OL,3,CHow is climate change and river
OL,4,Cpollution shaking up the Senedd
OL,5,CElection?
OL,7,FHowever, as climate change deepens
OL,8,Facross the world, and concerns about
OL,9,Fthe protection of our natural
OL,10,Fenvironment grow, some voters say that
OL,11,Fthey will support the party who will
OL,12,Fdo the most to tackle those issues.
OL,14,FEarlier this month, Scott Hardacre
OL,15,Ffrom Caerphilly was on a morning walk
OL,16,Fwith his dog when he noticed a pungent
OL,17,Fsmell in the air and saw the colours
OL,18,Fof a fuel spill in the river.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
