PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1777039866
OL,3,CHow is climate change and river
OL,4,Cpollution shaking up the Senedd
OL,5,CElection?
OL,7,FSouth Wales Fire and Rescue Service
OL,8,Ftold local people that they were aware
OL,9,Fof a strong smell of petrol in the
OL,10,Farea.
OL,12,FNatural Resources Wales said they were
OL,13,Fdealing with the incident and
OL,14,Finvestigating. But Scott said that he
OL,15,Fwill vote for a party that is serious
OL,16,Fabout reducing incidents of water
OL,17,Fpollution.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
