PN,46204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1777039866
OL,3,CHow is climate change and river
OL,4,Cpollution shaking up the Senedd
OL,5,CElection?
OL,7,F"In terms of what I'd be voting for,"
OL,8,Fsaid Scott. "Someone with a bit more
OL,9,Fenforcement of these types of issues.
OL,10,FI'm far from an environmentalist. But
OL,11,Fit does frustrate me the state on our
OL,12,Frivers, and just the general
OL,13,Fcleanliness of the area as well."
OL,15,FBut experts say that water pollution
OL,16,Fis not the only threat to our natural
OL,17,Fenvironment. They say the impact of
OL,18,Fclimate change is one of the biggest
OL,19,Fthreats that Wales faces.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
