OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1777039866
OL,3,CHow is climate change and river
OL,4,Cpollution shaking up the Senedd
OL,5,CElection?
OL,7,FSince the last Senedd election, Wales
OL,8,Fhas been hit by severe storms
OL,9,Fincluding Bert and Claudia. Last
OL,10,FNovember Storm Claudia brought the
OL,11,Fworst flooding Monmouth had seen in 40
OL,12,Fyears.
OL,14,FIn November 2024 Storm Bert brought a
OL,15,Frepeat of the flooding in Pontypridd
OL,16,Fthat the town had seen in Storm Dennis
OL,17,Fin February 2020.
OL,19,FJosh Downes is a barber with a shop on
OL,20,FPontypridd's Mill Street.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1777039866
OL,3,CHow is climate change and river
OL,4,Cpollution shaking up the Senedd
OL,5,CElection?
OL,7,FHe said he has never voted in a Senedd
OL,8,Felection before. But after being
OL,9,Fflooded in successive storms, he is
OL,10,Fgoing to vote at the 2026 Senedd
OL,11,Felection, and he will vote for a party
OL,12,Fwho will do more for victims of
OL,13,Fclimate change.
OL,15,F"The thing is, you don't want anybody
OL,16,Fto come forward and say they're going
OL,17,Fto do it then not follow that
OL,18,Fthrough," said Josh. You want someone
OL,19,Fwho takes it seriously. It's not just
OL,20,Fclimate change.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1777039866
OL,3,CHow is climate change and river
OL,4,Cpollution shaking up the Senedd
OL,5,CElection?
OL,7,F"It's the sort of effects after it.
OL,8,FIt's the flooding and the lives it
OL,9,Fdamages from the outside. And it does
OL,10,Fchange your life. Because it sort of
OL,11,Fputs you in a position where...well
OL,12,Ffor me, I was in a position where I
OL,13,Fwas financially destroyed."
OL,15,FExperts also say that it is not just
OL,16,Fin urban areas and near rivers where
OL,17,Fclimate change poses a threat.
OL,19,FEarlier this month another landslide
OL,20,Fon the Llyn Peninsula near Morfa Nefyn
OL,21,Fsaw roads closed and footpaths shut.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
