OL,3,CHow is climate change and river
OL,4,Cpollution shaking up the Senedd
OL,5,CElection?
OL,7,FRichard Bryant is a geologist who has
OL,8,Fmoved to the area from the South coast
OL,9,Fof England, where coastal erosion and
OL,10,Flandslides were even more frequent.
OL,12,FHe said that residents will want more
OL,13,Fhelp from the next Welsh Government.
OL,15,F"They've put a few regulations in
OL,16,Fobviously about driving across the
OL,17,Fbeach, but also using the coast path,
OL,18,Fthat's been shut as well," said
OL,19,FRichard.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1777039866
OL,3,CHow is climate change and river
OL,4,Cpollution shaking up the Senedd
OL,5,CElection?
OL,7,F"I think it's just part of living on a
OL,8,Fcoastline which is unstable. If they
OL,9,Fcan put in sort of various things to
OL,10,Fstop it happening like on the Isle of
OL,11,FWight. But a lot depends on the value
OL,12,Fof the land as well."
OL,14,FIn the Welsh capital, Dr Jennifer
OL,15,FAllan is a lecturer in global politics
OL,16,Fat Cardiff University.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
