PN,46210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1777039866
OL,3,CHow is climate change and river
OL,4,Cpollution shaking up the Senedd
OL,5,CElection?
OL,7,FShe teaches students about the
OL,8,Fpotential effects of climate change on
OL,9,FWales and the world. But she is unsure
OL,10,Fabout how many voters will think about
OL,11,Fit in the polling booth.
OL,13,F"For voters, for everybody, climate
OL,14,Fchange is sort of stealthy," said
OL,15,FJennifer. "It's one of those things
OL,16,Fthat's sort of slow and hidden
OL,17,Fsometimes.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1777039866
OL,3,CHow is climate change and river
OL,4,Cpollution shaking up the Senedd
OL,5,CElection?
OL,7,F"And it's not until you see an
OL,8,Femergency, or a major flood, or a
OL,9,Fheatwave that people start thinking
OL,10,Fabout it. And of course those things
OL,11,Fdon't necessarily time with when an
OL,12,Felection might be happening.
OL,14,F"So it can be really hard for voters
OL,15,Fto remember climate change when they
OL,16,Fgo to the ballot box."
OL,18,FSo what are the six main parties
OL,19,Ffighting for votes in the Senedd
OL,20,Felection promising on the environment?
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1777039866
OL,3,CHow is climate change and river
OL,4,Cpollution shaking up the Senedd
OL,5,CElection?
OL,7,FThe Welsh Greens say they will "build
OL,8,Fa cleaner greener economy that works
OL,9,Fwith nature not against it".
OL,11,FWelsh Labour say they will "build a
OL,12,Fgreener Wales by cleaning up our
OL,13,Frivers and seas."
OL,15,FPlaid Cymru say they will "make a new
OL,16,FClimate and Nature Action Plan."
OL,18,FThe Welsh Conservatives say they will
OL,19,F"scrap Natural Resources Wales and
OL,20,Freplace it with an independent
OL,21,Fregulator."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1777039866
OL,3,CHow is climate change and river
OL,4,Cpollution shaking up the Senedd
OL,5,CElection?
OL,7,FReform UK Wales say they will also
OL,8,F"abolish Natural Resources Wales and
OL,9,Fscrap net zero targets."
OL,11,FAnd the Welsh Liberal Democrats say
OL,12,Fthey will "lead Wales to net
OL,13,Fzero...making sure that no household
OL,14,Fis left behind in the transition."
OL,16,FUltimately, it is now down to us who
OL,17,Fwe want to vote for, and there are
OL,18,Fless than two weeks to go before
OL,19,Fpolling day on May 7th.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G13/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
